issuesFound.explanation:
The navigation link that represents the current page is styled as active but does not have aria‑current="page", so AT users cannot know which page they are on.  
Fix (inside the map where item.current is true):  
Replace:  
```tsx
<a
  href={item.href}
  className={['nav-link', item.current ? 'nav-link--current' : ''].filter(Boolean).join(' ')}
>
  {item.label}
</a>
```  
With:  
```tsx
<a
  href={item.href}
  className={['nav-link', item.current ? 'nav-link--current' : ''].filter(Boolean).join(' ')}
  aria-current={item.current ? 'page' : undefined}
>
  {item.label}
</a>
```  

